{"total":35,"pageSize":12,"pageCount":3,"data":[{"title":"最佳下饭奖：微信读书的「自动阅读」功能","uid":"3e17e6bbfd6f5e08bdf8e7844f42d67f","slug":"weread-autoslide","date":"2022-02-18T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-29T09:01:45.389Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/weread-autoslide.json","cover":"https://s2.loli.net/2022/06/29/9XPI5Qa17y8UnVG.png","text":"自动阅读，其实就是自动竖向滚动播放，能够让我们在阅读的时候解放双手，不需要反复去划动屏幕翻页。这一点尤其适合一个人吃饭无聊的时候使用。 此功能可以调节滚动速度，适合不同阅读速度的人、阅读不同的书，以及不同的吃饭节奏。 相比起吃饭看视频而言，我最近深刻觉得吃饭看书更舒服。视频节奏一...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":221,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"软件推荐","slug":"软件推荐","count":3,"path":"api/categories/软件推荐.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"阅读","slug":"阅读","count":7,"path":"api/tags/阅读.json"},{"name":"工具","slug":"工具","count":4,"path":"api/tags/工具.json"}],"author":{"name":"桌沿","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/me.png","link":"/","description":"桌沿奇思 Newsletter 主理人，少数派签约作者","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"sspai":{"icon":"/svg/sspai.svg","link":"https://sspai.com/u/379wzx2e/posts"},"jike":{"icon":"/svg/jike.svg","link":"https://okjk.co/IktPrE"},"youtube":{"icon":"/svg/youtube.svg","link":"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDHwHAiT-jJ4AACLHir70Fg"},"twitter":{"icon":"/svg/twitter.svg","link":"https://twitter.com/desksidezhuoyan"},"ins":{"icon":"/svg/instagram.svg","link":"https://www.instagram.com/deskside.zhuoyan/"},"mailto":{"icon":"/svg/mailto.svg","link":"mailto:deskside.zhuoyan@outlook.com"}}}},"feature":true},{"title":"换一种说法，换一种心态","uid":"3c3ffd4048039d3e6f849faa3a8ccdb9","slug":"change-the-way-of-talking-and-change-everything","date":"2022-02-18T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-29T09:10:02.318Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/change-the-way-of-talking-and-change-everything.json","cover":"https://s2.loli.net/2022/06/29/MiP7DYCoEb1xmlc.png","text":"近来，在阅读很多书籍的时候，都发现了「变换说法」的技巧。这种技巧来源于心理学和认知学，通过变更说话的形式，来改变我们对自己的心理暗示，进而在实质的行动层面也开始慢慢发生变更